This paper deals with online trading, which is a topic that falls under game theory (cs.GT) and algorithms (cs.DS). The problem of selecting the best possible buyer or seller is similar to the secretary problem, which is a classic problem in decision theory and optimization (cs.AI). The paper also discusses competitive algorithms, which is a topic in machine learning and optimization (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with the concept of welfare and gain-from-trade, which is related to information theory and communication (cs.IT).
